(9926, 'Rivotril 2mg 30 tab.', 'ريفوتريل 2مجم 30 قرص', '', '19', 'Clonazepam', 'F.hoffman la roche > egyptian pharmaceutical trading company', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Anti-epileptic.benzodiazepines', '2mg', 'Clonazepam is indicated as monotherapy or as an adjunct in the treatment of Lennox-Gastaut syndrome (petit mal variant), akinetic, and myoclonic seizures.[FDA Label][F3787] Furthermore, clonazepam may also be of some value in patients with absence spells (petit mal) who have failed to respond to succinimides.[FDA Label][F3787] Additionally, clonazepam is also indicated for the treatment of panic disorder, with or without agoraphobia, as defined in the DSM-V.[FDA Label]
